BlockSource: http://rsssf.com/tablesm/mex1903.html
Season: 1902-1903
Competition: Liga Mexicana de Foot-ball Amateur Association

*Inaugural Season
*On july of 1902 was created the first soccer league in Mexico, five teams took part:

*Pachuca Athletic Club 
*Orizaba Athletic Club 
*Reforma Athletic Club      [Mexico City] 
*British Club               [Mexico City]
*México Cricket Club SPLP   [Mexico City]
*SPLP: San Pedro de los Pinos 

*Tournament played at single leg

Round: 1

10/19/1902; México Cricket Club; 1-5; British Club; Campo San Pedro de los Pinos

Round: 2

11/1/1902; Pachuca AC; 3-3; Reforma AC; Campo Pachuca

Round: 3

11/30/1902; Reforma AC; 5-0; México Cricket Club; Club Reforma

Round: 4

12/8/1902; British Club; 2-0; Pachuca AC; Campo British Club

Round: 5

12/14/1902; Orizaba AC; 1-0; British Club; Campo Orizaba

Round: 6

12/20/1902; Pachuca AC; 0-0; México Cricket Club; Campo Pachuca

Round: 7

12/8/1902; Reforma AC; 1-0; British Club; Club Reforma

Round 8

1/1/1903; Pachuca AC; 0-1; Orizaba AC; Campo Pachuca

Round 9

1/12/1903; Orizaba AC; 2-2; Reforma AC; Campo Orizaba

Round 10

2/1/1903; Orizaba AC; W-L; México Cricket Club; Campo Orizaba
Forfeit
*Match awarded to Orizaba 1-0; México Cricket Club did not show up


